OL,3,CBolton's Winter Olympics hero on life
OL,4,Cin the spotlight
OL,6,FBolton's Winter Olympics hero Huw
OL,7,FNightingale has admitted he is still
OL,8,Fgetting used to his new-found fame.
OL,10,FHuw became an overnight celebrity
OL,11,Fafter winning Great Britain's first
OL,12,Fever gold medal on snow at the Milano
OL,13,FCortina games in February.
OL,15,FHe's since been recognised on the
OL,16,FLondon Underground and has even posed
OL,17,Ffor photographs with Noel Gallagher.
OL,19,F"I think the tube in London was quite
OL,20,Fa random place," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
