CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777457195
OL,3,CBolton's Winter Olympics hero on life
OL,4,Cin the spotlight
OL,6,F"I was sat on the underground and
OL,7,Fsomebody came up and showed me the
OL,8,Fnewspaper. I had my medal with me. I
OL,9,Fshowed it and everybody got quite
OL,10,Fexcited.
OL,12,F"You get used to people coming up to
OL,13,Fyou and congratulating you and taking
OL,14,Fpictures. But it was quite strange the
OL,15,Ffirst few weeks going from a normal
OL,16,Fathlete to kind of now - like a
OL,17,Fhousehold name kind of situation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
