FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777457195
OL,3,CBolton's Winter Olympics hero on life
OL,4,Cin the spotlight
OL,6,FHuw was invited by Manchester City to
OL,7,Fthe recent Premier League clash with
OL,8,FArsenal and as a devoted Blue, he
OL,9,Fmingled with the likes of City legend
OL,10,FMike Summerbee and Oasis star Noel.
OL,12,F"It was just a quick, quick
OL,13,Fphotograph. It was just at half-time
OL,14,Fso I didn't have that much time to
OL,15,Ftalk to him. But just to be in the
OL,16,Fsame area was just an amazing thing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
