CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777457195
OL,3,CBolton's Winter Olympics hero on life
OL,4,Cin the spotlight
OL,6,FHuw won gold with teammate Charlotte
OL,7,FBanks in the Mixed Team Snowboard
OL,8,FCross event, helping Team GB to record
OL,9,Fits best ever medal haul with three
OL,10,Fgolds and five medals in total.
OL,12,F"The Winter Olympics is one of the
OL,13,Fbiggest sporting events that there is
OL,14,Fand here in the UK we're not the
OL,15,Fbiggest winter nation," he said. "This
OL,16,Fyear has shown that what we've done
OL,17,Fhas shone a lot more light on winter
OL,18,Fsports and snowboard cross in general.
OL,19,FSo that's amazing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
