PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777457195
OL,3,CBolton's Winter Olympics hero on life
OL,4,Cin the spotlight
OL,6,FHuw moved from Bolton to Austria at
OL,7,Fthe age of five but makes regular
OL,8,Ftrips back to the North West.
OL,10,FHe recently dropped into The Snow
OL,11,FCentre Manchester to catch up with the
OL,12,Fman who set him on the path to gold,
OL,13,FDanny Chambers. The two met on the ski
OL,14,Fslopes a decade ago and Danny,
OL,15,Fcoincidentally also from Bolton,
OL,16,Fbecame Huw's first coach.
OL,18,F"He was 15 when he joined us," said
OL,19,FDanny.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777457195
OL,3,CBolton's Winter Olympics hero on life
OL,4,Cin the spotlight
OL,6,F"He was a bit of a wild child to begin
OL,7,Fwith - well he still is now! We did a
OL,8,Fbit of snowboarding, managed to get
OL,9,Fhim on some podiums. He did lots of
OL,10,Fraces across Europe. He just lived his
OL,11,Fown dream."
OL,13,FHuw remains in close contact with his
OL,14,Fold coach.
OL,16,F"Your first coach always stays with
OL,17,Fyou the most because he taught me how
OL,18,Fto do most of the things that I do
OL,19,Fnow," said Huw.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777457195
OL,3,CBolton's Winter Olympics hero on life
OL,4,Cin the spotlight
OL,6,F"So now we have a special bond.
OL,7,FWithout him I wouldn't be standing
OL,8,Fhere with a gold medal right now."
OL,10,FDanny was on a family ski holiday when
OL,11,FHuw won his gold medal.
OL,13,F"It was one of the greatest moments of
OL,14,Fmy life - apart from my kids being
OL,15,Fborn. I was actually sat on a mountain
OL,16,Fwatching with my little boys. I was
OL,17,Fshouting and screaming and every one
OL,18,Fthought I was a right weirdo!"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777457195
OL,3,CBolton's Winter Olympics hero on life
OL,4,Cin the spotlight
OL,6,FDanny, an accomplished snowboarder
OL,7,Fhimself, is now working alongside the
OL,8,FNightingale family to help discover
OL,9,Fthe next generation of boarders.
OL,11,FHe hopes the programme Boost SBX will
OL,12,Fprovide a pathway to the very top.
OL,14,F"Whether they've got experience
OL,15,Fracing, whether they've just got on a
OL,16,Fsnowboard for the first time, if they
OL,17,Fsee Huw and think 'I want that as my
OL,18,Fdream, I want to get to the Olympics'
OL,19,Fthen come and see us, because that's
OL,20,Fwhere we'll help get them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
